          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The TiT thin film target of this experiment",
                "was provided by a company (SODERN) in France. Backing",
                "material was Cu with a thickness of 1.2 mm and a",
                "diameter of 2.54 cm. Ti was deposited on Cu with an",
                "areal density of from 200 to 300 mu-g/cm2 and tritium",
                "was impregnated into Ti.",
                "The control of the beam energy and the stability for",
                "terminal voltage was performed by the resonance of",
                "991+-1 keV in 27Al(p,gamma) and that of 3047+-1 keV",
                "in 16O(alpha,alpha)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
